SELECT
    `TPC-DS Benchmark Model`.`d_product_brand_id`              AS `d_product_brand_id`,
    `TPC-DS Benchmark Model`.`d_product_brand_name`            AS `d_product_brand_name`,
    `TPC-DS Benchmark Model`.`d_product_manufacturer_id`       AS `d_product_manufacturer_id`,
    `TPC-DS Benchmark Model`.`d_product_manufacturer_name`     AS `d_product_manufacturer_name`,
    SUM( `TPC-DS Benchmark Model`.`m_ss_ext_sales_price_sum` ) AS `sum_m_ss_ext_sales_price_sum_ok`
FROM
    `tpc-ds benchmark model`.`tpc-ds benchmark model` `TPC-DS Benchmark Model`
WHERE
    ( (
            CASE
                WHEN ( `TPC-DS Benchmark Model`.`d_store_zip_code` <>
                        `TPC-DS Benchmark Model`.`d_customer_zip_code` )
                THEN true
                ELSE false
            END )
    AND (
            `TPC-DS Benchmark Model`.`Sold Calendar Year` = 1999 )
    AND (
            `TPC-DS Benchmark Model`.`Sold d_month_of_year` = 11 )
    AND (
            `TPC-DS Benchmark Model`.`d_product_manager_id` = 8 ) )
GROUP BY
    1,
    2,
    3,
    4
ORDER BY
    5 DESC ,
    2 ,
    1 ,
    3 ,
    4 LIMIT 100
